  <h2>1. This is a demonstration</h2>
  <p>
    Flipkart Assist is a portfolio project built to demonstrate multi-agent AI and
    retrieval-augmented search. It is <strong>not a store</strong>. No product shown can
    actually be purchased here, no order is fulfilled, and no payment is processed —
    the checkout flow ends in a mock confirmation.
  </p>

  <h2>2. No affiliation with Flipkart</h2>
  <p>
    This project is not affiliated with, endorsed by, sponsored by, or connected to
